## Build & Test (read by pipeline agents — keep exact and current)

```bash
# Build
xcodebuild build -scheme {{SCHEME}} -destination 'platform=iOS Simulator,name={{SIM_DEVICE}}'

# Full test suite (the pass/fail contract for issue-worker)
xcodebuild test -scheme {{SCHEME}} -destination 'platform=iOS Simulator,name={{SIM_DEVICE}}'
```

- Scheme: `{{SCHEME}}` · Simulator: `{{SIM_DEVICE}}` · Min deployment target: `{{MIN_IOS}}`
- Test frameworks: {{SWIFT_TESTING_OR_XCTEST}}
- Conventions agents must follow: {{ARCHITECTURE_NOTES — e.g. "SwiftUI + @Observable, no new dependencies without an issue saying so"}}

## Agent pipeline

This repo is on the [indie-app-autopilot](https://github.com/rshankras/indie-app-autopilot) pipeline.
Issue labels drive the queue (`agent-ready` → `agent-in-progress` → PR). Agents obey the
[safety contract](https://github.com/rshankras/indie-app-autopilot/blob/main/docs/SAFETY.md):
never merge, never push to main, tests green before any PR.
